snippet.textDisplay: As someone who worked at Dunkin Donuts, it's an 80-20 Mix of by hand and by machine. For filled donuts, including jelly and cream, you have to use a machine to get proper filling, but it's under your control so you can 100% explode donuts with too much filling. Glazed donuts are by hand, so are all toppings and frostings.
